{"id":619265,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/10/【立此存照】鞍山公安：一男子公然侮辱阅兵式官/","date":"2019-10-02T06:07:18Z","modified":"2019-10-06T06:12:49Z","title":"【立此存照】鞍山公安：一男子公然侮辱阅兵式 警方重拳出击","content":"<p>10月1日上午，鞍山网警接到网民举报，鞍山籍网民“俊小哥”在微信群中发表侮辱国庆阅兵的恶意言论，引发广大网民的极大愤慨。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/a_364164970805456896.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-619268\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/a_364164970805456896.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"822\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/a_364164970805456896.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/a_364164970805456896-183x300.jpg 183w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/a_364164970805456896-623x1024.jpg 623w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/a_364164973632417792.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-619269\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/a_364164973632417792.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"771\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/a_364164973632417792.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/a_364164973632417792-195x300.jpg 195w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/a_364164976790728704.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-619270\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/a_364164976790728704.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"766\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/a_364164976790728704.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/a_364164976790728704-196x300.jpg 196w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/a_364164979483471872.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-619271\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/a_364164979483471872.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"762\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/a_364164979483471872.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/a_364164979483471872-197x300.jpg 197w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>鞍山市公安局铁东分局根据网民举报线索，迅速开展调查核实工作。经查，10月1日上午，网民“俊小哥”（真实姓名高某俊，男，37岁，鞍山市铁东区大孤山街道人）在微信群与他人聊天中发表针对国庆70周年阅兵的恶意言论。随后，民警将高某俊传唤到案，高某俊对自己的违法行为供认不讳。根据《中华人民共和国治安管理处罚法》第二十六条和《中华人民共和国网络安全法》第十二条、第七十条之规定，鞍山市公安局铁东分局依法给予高某俊拘留十五天的行政处罚。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/a_364164982327209984.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-619266\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/a_364164982327209984.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/a_364164982327209984.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/a_364164982327209984-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>鞍山公安警情通报</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/92457a3f273bafa1a0fe56ab7354f554.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-619267\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/92457a3f273bafa1a0fe56ab7354f554.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"282\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/92457a3f273bafa1a0fe56ab7354f554.jpg 852w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/92457a3f273bafa1a0fe56ab7354f554-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/92457a3f273bafa1a0fe56ab7354f554-768x433.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>警方提醒：</strong>网络非法外之地，网民在网络上的言行要恪守真实客观，注重网上道德，遵守国家的有关法律法规，承担因自己的行为而引起的法律责任，逞一时口快，换来的将是法律的严惩。</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[38912,38920,38960],"tags":[39038,39003,9212,10310]}